   (OPTIONAL SIDEBAR FOLLOWS.)
</P>
<P>
   SIDEBAR: OBI-WAN AND THEN SOME
</P>
<P>
   Most of Alec Guinness' best films can be found on videocassette,
and a few on laser disk or DVD. A greatest-hits sampling might
include the following six films:
