<HEADLINE>
ON THE LANGUAGE OF CERVANTES, THE IMPRINT OF THE INTERNET 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 By SAM DILLON   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
