<P>
   COXNET PTECH 0808 _ Gadgets once relegated to home entertainment
are now the ultimate travel accessories. Video games, DVD players
and even the PC are moving out of the home and onto the road, which
has made owning a simple CD or cassette player for your set of
wheels last century's news. (Stupp, Dayton Daily News) Art includes
a 4-column color photo of car stereo installers looking over a new
DVD player in a car.
</P>
