written for kids to understand. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   NFK-MIDDLE-SCHOOL _ A feature on starting middle school and
advice from some seventh graders who have made the transition.
(Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
