<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-07 15:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4774 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r s BC-FBC-STANFORD-HNS &LR;      08-07 0830
