<P>
   SCIENCE-MEDICINE
</P>
<P>
   CONSUMERS-HMO _ I want my HMO. That's the cry of hundreds of
Georgia seniors who have seen their Medicare HMO plans _ plans that
offered them annual physicals, vision tests and cheap prescriptions
_ evaporate within the past two years. It's a national crisis
brought on by low government reimbursement and rising health care
costs. And although there are 10 proposed laws to fix the
situation, it's leaving a lot of elderly with a traditional
Medicare plan _ with all those traditionally uncovered costs _ like
those very expensive drugs. With a tip box on what to do if your
plan suddenly folds. (Lore, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
<P>
   HEALTH-WATER _ Health benefits of drinking water, why you need
to, how much you should drink. (Walker, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
<P>
   EDs: With box on foods that have a lot of water content and
photo.
</P>
