 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; MONEYBAG:  &LR;  Q:My wife and I both work, and we plan to place our son
in day care. We will pay about $360 per month. How much of a tax
break would we get? I've heard about the dependent care tax credit
but don't understand it. &UR; COLUMN BY ARTHUR LOUIS &QL;  &LR;
